          <p><a href="/oval-engagement-rings/">Browse oval engagement rings</a></p>

          <h3>Emerald Cut Moissanite Rings</h3>
          <p>Emerald cut moissanite shows a distinctive hall-of-mirrors effect in the step-cut facets. At this cut, the moissanite's rainbow fire is more subtle - the long facets show depth over flash, which suits the architectural aesthetic of emerald cut design.</p>
          <p><a href="/emerald-cut-engagement-rings/">Browse emerald cut rings</a></p>

